    "faq": {
      "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
      "q1": "Is StrikeAhead really free?",
      "a1": "Yes! The Free plan is free forever. You can log up to 10 catches per month, use AI species recognition and read the community feed. Upgrade anytime, cancel monthly.",
      "q2": "Which platforms is the app available on?",
      "a2": "StrikeAhead runs as a web app in any browser (desktop & mobile), as a native iOS app on the App Store and as an Android app on Google Play. All platforms are fully synchronised.",
      "q3": "How accurate are the AI catch predictions?",
      "a3": "Prediction accuracy improves with every logged catch. Our model combines your personal catch history with weather data, solunar phases, tide calendars and community data. After about 20 catches, predictions are significantly personalised.",
      "q4": "Which countries does the Licence Manager support?",
      "a4": "Currently Germany, Austria, Switzerland, Netherlands, Belgium, France, Spain, Portugal, Italy, Croatia, Poland, Denmark, Sweden and Norway. More countries are being added.",
      "q5": "Are my GPS data and fishing spots shared?",
      "a5": "Never without your permission. Every catch is private by default. You decide what to share with the community. GPS coordinates are encrypted and never passed to third parties.",
      "q6": "Can I use StrikeAhead as a fishing coach?",
      "a6": "Yes! With the Legend plan you can create your coaching profile, take on students, manage bookings and even host your own tournaments."
    },
